reviews.text: One of the few choices in the mid field boarding area. Reasonably priced,  highly recommend the Korean spicy noodles with spam and egg, a great comfort food before one's flight (particular of you're flying budget airlines and don't intend to eat on board)

It is one of the three restaurants near gate 210 area. Ordered teriyaki chicken rice and pizza. The chicken rice is just so so , topped with a very very thick sauce. However, the pizza is incredibly good. It is freshly baked so have to wait a bit longer. Crispy and crunchy for the edge and base. For this size and price for a whole pizza at the airport, it is very fair.

Was hungry after getting of the plane.  Found this place the prices were decent . The wonton soup tasted very good the aroma was so different then other places I have tried.
The Ramen was extremely delicious the ramen had a Seafood flavor. The spam was very delicious totally different comparing it to the states or Canada spam.
The rice and chicken were dry but their honey lemon tea was great.
Quick and affordable food is decent

reviews.text:
인생에서 가장 가성비 떨어지고 형편없는 음식을 먹었습니다.
피자 추천하지 않습니다. 도우랑 치즈는 딱딱하게 굳은 상태고  플라스틱 포크랑 나이프를 줘 먹기도 불편했으며, 혼잡하고 서빙은 패스트푸드점의 셀프 서비스입니다, 결정적으로 $85달러의 거금이 들어갔는데도 불구하고 돼지고기 고명은 가장 싼 돈전지 구이더군요. 퍽퍽한 그 살 생각하시면 됩니다. 토마토소스는 그림에서는 그렇게 뿌려놓고 음식에서는 보이지도 않았습니다.
이 가게가 영업되는것이 첵랍콕의 오점이라고 가감없이 표현하겠습니다. 옆의 아지센 가세요. 적어도 다른 메뉴 시키세요.비행기 연착으로 제공받은 밀 바우처의 $80을 뺀 딱 $5달러만큼의 식사를 했습니다.

One of the few choices in the mid field boarding area. Reasonably priced,  highly recommend the Korean spicy noodles with spam and egg, a great comfort food before one's flight (particular of you're flying budget airlines and don't intend to eat on board)
其實跟其它美心MX的水準差不多，但價格偏貴可能在機場面吧！坐位不太多，經常人滿。

It is one of the three restaurants near gate 210 area. Ordered teriyaki chicken rice and pizza. The chicken rice is just so so , topped with a very very thick sauce. However, the pizza is incredibly good. It is freshly baked so have to wait a bit longer. Crispy and crunchy for the edge and base. For this size and price for a whole pizza at the airport, it is very fair.
普通，真的食物與收銀處的相有大距離，少很多

reviews.text: On the whole a very good airport. Security is quick and efficient, and passport control is normally very quick too. There are a good selection of places to eat, despite ongoing renovations. The internal transit system is easy to use. No complaints.

One of the Large airports in the world. Its very wonderful shape of airport. Staffs are so friendly and helpful to passengers. The airport is very clean and fully well maintained. The view of airport is incredible. My experience was great here...

Great airport in town. Large varieties of food and great service at the Check In counter. Fast passenger flow. The terminals are large and comfy as well. The problems are the food can be quite expensive, and you may expect to walk a lot inside the airport. Also, it is far from Downtown, so you may catch a taxi or hop onto the Airport Express. Still pretty great tho. 4/5

Incredible!!! One of the amazing airports in the world. I don't know how it comes to their mind to build up an airport like this place. Its very big and wonderful shape airport. Staffs are so friendly and helpful to passengers. The airport is very clean and fully well maintained. The view of airport is incredible. My experience was great here. I was totally surprised. Love it❤

One of the best airports I have ever been. I fell in love with their relaxation corner in terminal 1. They are silent with ambient temperature and smooth lights. Even the room is perfumed with a soft smell of eucalyptus. They even have charging ports right next to the comfortable beds. With an amazing view of aircraft through the glass wall on one side.
